ABYSSAL_MINER.name: Abyssal Miner
ABYSSAL_MINER.spawnMessage: An Abyssal Miner breaks out of the water!

AGARIMOO.name: Agarimoo
AGARIMOO.spawnMessage: Your Chumcap Bucket trembles, it's an Agarimoo.

BLOATED_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.name: Mithril Grubber
BLOATED_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.spawnMessage: A leech of the mines surfaces... you've caught a Bloated Mithril Grubber.

BLUE_SHARK.name: Blue Shark
BLUE_SHARK.spawnMessage: You spot a fin as blue as the water it came from, it's a Blue Shark.

CARROT_KING.name: Carrot King
CARROT_KING.spawnMessage: Is this even a fish? It's the Carrot King!

DEEP_SEA_PROTECTOR.name: Deep Sea Protector
DEEP_SEA_PROTECTOR.spawnMessage: You have awoken the Deep Sea Protector, prepare for a battle!

FIRE_EEL.name: Fire Eel
FIRE_EEL.spawnMessage: A Fire Eel slithers out from the depths.

FLAMING_WORM.name: Flaming Worm
FLAMING_WORM.spawnMessage: A Flaming Worm surfaces from the depths!

FROSTY.name: Frosty
FROSTY.spawnMessage: It's a snowman! He looks harmless.

FROZEN_STEVE.name: Frozen Steve
FROZEN_STEVE.spawnMessage: Frozen Steve fell into the pond long ago, never to resurface...until now!

GREAT_WHITE_SHARK.name: Great White Shark
GREAT_WHITE_SHARK.spawnMessage: Hide no longer, a Great White Shark has tracked your scent and thirsts for your blood!

GRIM_REAPER.name: Grim Reaper
GRIM_REAPER.spawnMessage: This can't be! The manifestation of death himself!

GRINCH.name: Grinch
GRINCH.spawnMessage: The Grinch stole Jerry's Gifts...get them back!

GUARDIAN_DEFENDER.name: Guardian Defender
GUARDIAN_DEFENDER.spawnMessage: You've discovered a Guardian Defender of the sea.

LARGE_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.name: Mithril Grubber
LARGE_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.spawnMessage: A leech of the mines surfaces... you've caught a Large Mithril Grubber.

LAVA_BLAZE.name: Lava Blaze
LAVA_BLAZE.spawnMessage: A Lava Blaze has surfaced from the depths!

LAVA_FLAME.name: Lava Flame
LAVA_FLAME.spawnMessage: A Lava Flame flies out from beneath the lava.

LAVA_LEECH.name: Lava Leech
LAVA_LEECH.spawnMessage: A small but fearsome Lava Leech emerges.

LAVA_PIGMAN.name: Lava Pigman
LAVA_PIGMAN.spawnMessage: A Lava Pigman arose from the depths!

LORD_JAWBUS.name: Lord Jawbus
LORD_JAWBUS.spawnMessage: You have angered a legendary creature... Lord Jawbus has arrived

MAGMA_SLUG.name: Magma Slug
MAGMA_SLUG.spawnMessage: From beneath the lava appears a Magma Slug.

MEDIUM_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.name: Mithril Grubber
MEDIUM_MITHRIL_GRUBBER.spawnMessage: A leech of the mines surfaces... you've caught a Medium Mithril Grubber.

MITHRIL_GRUBBER.name: Mithril Grubber
MITHRIL_GRUBBER.spawnMessage: A leech of the mines surfaces... you've caught a Mithril Grubber.

MOOGMA.name: Moogma
MOOGMA.spawnMessage: You hear a faint Moo from the lava... A Moogma appears.

NIGHTMARE.name: Nightmare
NIGHTMARE.spawnMessage: You hear trotting from beneath the waves, you caught a Nightmare.

NIGHT_SQUID.name: Night Squid
NIGHT_SQUID.spawnMessage: Pitch Darkness reveals you've caught a Night Squid.

NURSE_SHARK.name: Nurse Shark
NURSE_SHARK.spawnMessage: A tiny fin emerges from the water, you've caught a Nurse Shark.

NUTCRACKER.name: Nutcracker
NUTCRACKER.spawnMessage: You found a forgotten Nutcracker laying beneath the ice.

OASIS RABBIT.name: Oasis Rabbit
OASIS RABBIT.spawnMessage: An Oasis Rabbit appears from the water.

OASIS SHEEP.name: Oasis Sheep
OASIS SHEEP.spawnMessage: An Oasis Sheep appears from the water.

PHANTOM_FISHER.name: Phantom Fisher
PHANTOM_FISHER.spawnMessage: The spirit of a long lost Phantom Fisher has come to haunt you.

PYROCLASTIC_WORM.name: Pyroclastic Worm
PYROCLASTIC_WORM.spawnMessage: You feel the heat radiating as a Pyroclastic Worm surfaces.

REINDRAKE.name: Reindrake
REINDRAKE.spawnMessage: WOAH! A Reindrake was summoned from the depths!

RIDER_OF_THE_DEEP.name: Rider of the Deep
RIDER_OF_THE_DEEP.spawnMessage: The Rider of the Deep has emerged.

SEA_ARCHER.name: Sea Archer
SEA_ARCHER.spawnMessage: You reeled in a Sea Archer.

SEA_EMPEROR.name: Sea Emperor
SEA_EMPEROR.spawnMessage: The Sea Emperor arises from the depths.

SEA_GUARDIAN.name: Sea Guardian
SEA_GUARDIAN.spawnMessage: You stumbled upon a Sea Guardian.

SEA_WITCH.name: Sea Witch

THUNDER.name: Thunder
THUNDER.spawnMessage: You hear a massive rumble as Thunder emerges.

TIGER_SHARK.name: Tiger Shark
TIGER_SHARK.spawnMessage: A striped beast bounds from the depths, the wild Tiger Shark!

WATER_HYDRA.name: Water Hydra
WATER_HYDRA.spawnMessage: The Water Hydra has come to test your strength.

WEREWOLF.name: Werewolf
WEREWOLF.spawnMessage: It must be a full moon, a Werewolf appears.

FROG_MAN.name: Frog Man
FROG_MAN.spawnMessage: Is it a frog? Is it a man? Well, yes, sorta, IT'S FROG MAN!!!!!!

BANSHEE.name: Banshee
BANSHEE.spawnMessage: The desolate wail of a Banshee breaks the silence.

DUMPSTER_DIVER.name: Dumpster Diver
DUMPSTER_DIVER.spawnMessage: A Dumpster Diver has emerged from the swamp!

TRASH_GOBBLER.name: Trash Gobbler
TRASH_GOBBLER.spawnMessage: The Trash Gobbler is hungry for you!

ALLIGATOR.name: Alligator
ALLIGATOR.spawnMessage: A long snout breaks the surface of the water. It's an Alligator!

SNAPPING_TURTLE.name: Snapping Turtle
SNAPPING_TURTLE.spawnMessage: A Snapping Turtle is coming your way, and it's ANGRY!

BAYOU_SLUDGE.name: Bayou Sludge
BAYOU_SLUDGE.spawnMessage: A swampy mass of slime emerges, the Bayou Sludge!

TITANOBOA.name: Titanoboa
TITANOBOA.spawnMessage: A massive Titanoboa surfaces. It's body stretches as far as the eye can see.

BLUE_RINGED_OCTOPUS.name: Blue Ringed Octopus
BLUE_RINGED_OCTOPUS.spawnMessage: A garish set of tentacles arise. It's a Blue Ringed Octopus!

WIKI_TIKI.name: Wiki Tiki
WIKI_TIKI.spawnMessage: The water bubbles and froths. A massive form emerges- you have disturbed the Wiki Tiki! You shall pay the price.

FRIED_CHICKEN.name: Fried Chicken
FRIED_CHICKEN.spawnMessage: Smells of burning. Must be a Fried Chicken.

FIREPROOF_WITCH.name: Fireproof Witch
FIREPROOF_WITCH.spawnMessage: Trouble's brewing, it's a Fireproof Witch!

FIERY_SCUTTLER.name: Fiery Scuttler
FIERY_SCUTTLER.spawnMessage: A Fiery Scuttler inconspicuously waddles up to you, friends in tow.

RAGNAROK.name: Ragnarok
RAGNAROK.spawnMessage: The sky darkens and the air thickens. The end times are upon us: Ragnarok is here.
